Valor

Valor provides information and an interface for interacting with non-custodial smart contracts on public blockchains. Valor does not custody user funds and is not a bank or financial advisor. Using smart contracts involves risk, including the possibility of losing funds. Always review transaction details in your wallet before confirming.
